query:
SELECT p.id, p.userId, p.firstName, p.lastName, p.email, u.id as userIdFromUsers
FROM participants p 
LEFT JOIN users u ON p.email = u.email
WHERE p.email = 's.sachs@sachs-media.com'
LIMIT 5;
